{"tid":1789991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想有女仔再俾人呃","createTime":"2019-12-19T16:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T16:36:14.000Z","uid":208257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc86809447ed7a0b88bfe0572a957fbcbab96408","tid":1789991,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該大家推出去<br />\n唔想有女仔再俾人呃</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">網上詐騙電視就見得多<br />\n大身邊朋友出事就真係好少見<br />\n<br />\n呢個人不得了啦<br />\n同其他人講及自己同前度有幾咁慘<br />\n博得其他人嘅同情<br />\n其實同時間同幾條女一齊<br />\n<br />\n再者 近期社會事件 佢話佢自己有份參與 仲要係前線分子 但係家庭背景係藍色 又話有經濟封鎖有收電話等等等 <br />\n<br />\n近期嘅三罷第一日得到佢朋友嘅資訊話佢俾人拉咗經過FC之後原來係屋企 只不過係熄佐電話 社交網站冇上線姐 期間仲要聯同自己嘅同黨去籌保釋金 但係其實一直都係屋企 <br />\n<br />\n再加上話自己俾人收電話期間 借咗人哋嘅電話 但係點知有借無還 網上面同人哋談判話幾時攞返部電話出嚟 約定左時間 但係放飛機 最後block人哋AC 仲要係自己哪既社交網站裏面講到自己啱晒咁樣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">估唔到而家仲有呢啲人嘅存在<br />\n為咗唔好再比其他人受欺騙<br />\n唔該睇到呢篇文嘅人share出去！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKp8viF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKp8viF.jpg&h=b46c9dde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtiM1qn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtiM1qn.jpg&h=49104a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmJ1QiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmJ1QiK.jpg&h=7292d802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f4a799148c42cd7957b0a28bc346fb5b5af860c","tid":1789991,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1元旦大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEffSro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEffSro.jpg&h=99a1f162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBcxEME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBcxEME.jpg&h=7ab8f960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKLvrrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKLvrrF.jpg&h=653d2ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mY6iAj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmY6iAj1.jpg&h=c159792d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tVOXym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tVOXym.jpg&h=2b5d9c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uVGNZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uVGNZR.jpg&h=abdc3b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50850b14201cbf02db5efc9abdffb94222d10844","tid":1789991,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e28cb1f3f706b39e681fd53805fb3ed9f8650faf","tid":1789991,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bb0bcc37e7cbe92a7b449c67201ec68682f6fe3","tid":1789991,"uid":208257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}